# 8_DigitRecognitionUsing_RandomForest

## Overview
This project implements a handwritten digit recognition system using the Random Forest classifier. The model classifies digits (0â€“9) from image pixel data.

## Workflow
- Load dataset (MNIST / sklearn digits)
- Preprocess images (flatten pixel values)
- Train Random Forest model
- Evaluate using accuracy and confusion matrix
- Visualize predictions

## Tech Stack
- Python
- NumPy
- Pandas
- Matplotlib
- Scikit-learn

## Applications
- OCR systems
- Bank cheque digit recognition
- Postal code recognition
